{"title":"拉丁美洲谚语","authors":["张铠"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":4,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊玩刀剑者，必死于刀剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊寻找就能找到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊自力更生，胜似上帝的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊愿望的东西必须伸手才能得到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊没有不带刺的玫瑰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊发光的并不都是金子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊有火就有灰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊信仰是团结的纽带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊只要迈步，总不迟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊沉睡的虾，只有被急流卷走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊心不会想没见过的东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊苍蝇不会飞进闭着的嘴里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊知识是经验的产儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊要想成功，必须走完从说到做这段距离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔张铠　译辑〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}